@startuml
title FastAPI Microservices High-Level Data Flow

actor Client

node "Docker Compose Network" {
  component "service_auth\nFastAPI" as Auth
  component "service_data\nFastAPI" as Data
}

database "Future Identity Store" as Identity
database "Future Persistent Store" as Storage

Client --> Auth : POST /api/v1/auth/token
Auth --> Client : JWT access token

Client --> Data : Bearer token\nCRUD requests\n
Data --> Auth : GET /api/v1/auth/introspect\nAuthorization + X-Internal-Api-Key
Auth --> Data : Token claims
Data --> Client : Protected API response

Auth --> Identity : Replace bootstrap credentials
Data --> Storage : Replace in-memory repository

@enduml
